## REST API Endpoints

All entities get standard RESTful endpoints:

```
GET    /api/{entities}          - Get all
GET    /api/{entities}/{id}     - Get by ID
POST   /api/{entities}          - Create
PUT    /api/{entities}/{id}     - Update
DELETE /api/{entities}/{id}     - Delete
```

