## Getting Started

### 1. Install Dependencies
```bash
dotnet restore
```

### 2. Setup Database
```bash
# Create PostgreSQL database
dotnet ef database update --startup-project src/WebApi
```

### 3. Run Application
```bash
dotnet run --project src/WebApi
```

The API will be available at `https://localhost:5001`
Swagger documentation: `https://localhost:5001/swagger`

## JWT Configuration

Configure JWT in `appsettings.json`:
```json
{
	"Jwt": {
		"Secret": "your-secret-key-min-32-chars",
		"Issuer": "{{ .Project.Name }}-api",
		"Audience": "{{ .Project.Name }}-client",
		"ExpirationMinutes": 60
	}
}
```

## Database Connection

PostgreSQL connection string in `appsettings.json`:
```
Host=localhost;Port=5432;Database={{ .Project.Name | snakecase }}_db;Username=postgres;Password=postgres
```

